No. 10-1310 (R46-020). Norex Petroleum Limited, Petitioner v. Access Industries, Inc., et al. 564 U.S. 1053, 133 S. Ct. 21,

180 L. Ed. 2d 913,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 5018. June 29, 2011.

The petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit in the above-entitled case was dismissed today pursuant to Rule 46.1 of the Rules of this Court.

Same case below, 631 F.3d 29.
